title: Beanie babies were the NFTs of the 90s
description:
What happens when the frenzy ends and the world doesn’t value your valuables? Vox’s Emily Stewart explains. 
Read Emily’s story: https://www.vox.com/the-goods/22870250/nft-beanie-baby-price-guide-bubble-princess-value

Today’s episode was produced by Taylor Maycan, engineered by Cristian Ayala and hosted by Adam Clark Estes.
